  "texts": [
    "However, blockchain's decentralised nature makes it challenging to apply these traditional legal frameworks to blockchain-based intellectual property (Kshetri 2018).",
    "Furthermore, the anonymity and pseudonymity of blockchain transactions create difficulties in identifying infringers and enforcing intellectual property rights.",
    "In traditional legal frameworks, infringers can be identified through their personal information and can be held accountable for their actions.",
    "However, on a decentralised blockchain network, the identity of the infringer may not be readily apparent, and therefore, enforcing IPRs can be challenging (Singh and Tripathi 2019).",
    "To address these challenges, several initiatives are underway to establish legal frameworks for the protection and enforcement of intellectual property rights on the blockchain."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "However, blockchain's decentralised nature makes it challenging to apply these traditional legal frameworks to blockchain-based intellectual property (Kshetri 2018).",
    "However, on a decentralised blockchain network, the identity of the infringer may not be readily apparent, and therefore, enforcing IPRs can be challenging (Singh and Tripathi 2019)."
  ]
